TEXT 504 168 Left 2 ;A model ("SW_vkn" in this case) shall be specified for the\nvoltage-controlled switch, where the main parameters are\nthe closed-resistance (Ron), the open-resistance (Roff) and\nthe on/off voltage (Vt). When the differential voltage across\nthe +/- pins exceeds Vt, the switch closes showing very low\nresistance; otherwise it stays open (thus very high resistance).\nNote that on Vout node a pull-up or pull-down resistor shall\nbe included in order not to keep the node floating while the\nswitch is open!
